        "text_tQNWNg": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>See the three Dry moisturisers: <a href=\"/products/dry-flow-moisturiser\" title=\"Flow — Dry, a light face moisturiser for dry skin\">Flow</a>, <a href=\"/products/core-dry-a-cushioning-body-moisturiser-for-dry-skin\" title=\"Core — Dry, a cushioning body moisturiser for dry skin\">Core</a> and <a href=\"/products/deep-dry-sensitive-a-rich-moisturiser-for-dry-sensitive-skin-for-hands-elbows-and-feet-copy\" title=\"Deep — Dry, a rich moisturiser for dry skin, for hands, elbows and feet\">Deep</a><br/></li><li>Not sure this is you? <a href=\"/pages/find-your-skin-type\" title=\"Find Your Skin Type\">Find your skin type</a><br/></li><li>The other skin types: <a href=\"/collections/dry-sensitive-skin-type\" title=\"Dry Sensitive Skin Type\">Dry Sensitive</a>, <a href=\"/collections/balanced-skin-type\" title=\"Balanced Skin Type\">Balanced</a>, <a href=\"/collections/oily\" title=\"Oily Skin Type\">Oily</a>, <a href=\"/collections/oily-sensitive\" title=\"Oily Sensitive Skin Type\">Oily Sensitive</a><br/></li><li><a href=\"/blogs/ingredients\" title=\"Ingredients\">How we choose our ingredients</a>, and the science behind them</li></ul>",
